about.summary: Client for the Ocean Biogeographic Information System (<https://obis.org>).

name: r-robis
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = '2.1.8' %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-robis
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/robis_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/robis/robis_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: b302dcea2b43bace157f7356234ef951fdd3dd46f251d5cb7f82edb1815726e2

build:
  merge_build_host: True  # [win]
  number: 2
  noarch: generic
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-dplyr
    - r-ggplot2
    - r-httr
    - r-jsonlite
    - r-leaflet
  run:
    - r-base
    - r-dplyr
    - r-ggplot2
    - r-httr
    - r-jsonlite
    - r-leaflet

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('robis')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('robis')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://github.com/iobis/robis
  license: MIT
  summary: Client for the Ocean Biogeographic Information System (<https://obis.org>).
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
    - ocefpaf
